{"tid":968540,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"貝拿度施華係咪癲Q咗","createTime":"2019-01-04T10:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T10:00:23.000Z","uid":165817,"like":259,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"69274d1f9853ba764ea0f690a554d7d5e6fdf86c","tid":968540,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"以前一直以為佢係好柔嗰啲技術型<br />\n尋晚成隻癲狗咁瘋狂逼搶<br />\n唔只體能好 仲好硬淨 下下埋去拍 埋去撼<br />\n上半場已經拍到韋拿度姆同軒達臣失方寸<br />\n<br />\n臨尾曼城啲人已經謝哂皮<br />\n甘賓尼抽筋 阿古路斬唔起 丹尼路撻Q<br />\n但B華補時仲喺前場瘋狂壓逼<br />\n逼完艾利臣逼洛夫雲 逼完老虎逼TAA<br />\n仲有球邊線熱誠飛剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賽後統計數字<br />\n貝拿度施華跑動咗超過13700米<br />\n打破咗今季英超紀錄<br />\n<br />\n雖然費南甸奴尋晚係上帝級演出<br />\n但英超官方MoM頒咗俾貝拿度施華<br />\n我都覺得絕對值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5131c940b271c814f1a944217971addd31b8cfdc","tid":968540,"uid":142351,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c65009ed490ad09ad563502a6552076f48a4411","tid":968540,"uid":51105,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"軒達臣唔拍都甩<br />\n擔泥佬撻Q好正常<br />\n呢兩個無說服力<br />\n<br />\n不過佢尋晚同費撚癲奴真係好fit"},{"pid":"650d1df177761ff397860d3fb957617f53460a16","tid":968540,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c65009ed490ad09ad563502a6552076f48a4411","tid":968540,"uid":51105,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"軒達臣唔拍都甩<br />\n擔泥佬撻Q好正常<br />\n呢兩個無說服力<br />\n<br />\n不過佢尋晚同費撚癲奴真係好fit"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d663a87c4cc57ea5811786cb78146a1d6570d4","tid":968540,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c65009ed490ad09ad563502a6552076f48a4411","tid":968540,"uid":51105,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T10:16:10